fishing_fraction:
SELECT fishing_points / active_positions as fishing_fraction, *  FROM [world-fishing-827:scratch_david_mmsi_lists.allyears_fishing_vessel_info] 
where nn_max_label_all != nn_max_label_fishing_all
and nn_max_score_all > .95
and fishing_points / active_positions < .1
and active_positions > 1000
and nn_max_label_all != "Reefer"
order by nn_max_score_all desc
